{"body":[{"content":"「字幕由 富睿字幕組 搬運」\n（禁止在B站宣傳漫遊相關内容，否則拉黑）","location":2,"from":0,"to":0.417},{"content":"「字幕由 富睿字幕組 搬運」\n（禁止在B站宣傳漫遊相關内容，否則拉黑）\n洋蔥火腿三明治1份160BC","from":0.417,"location":2,"to":3.833},{"content":"謝謝光臨","from":5.125,"location":2,"to":7.0},{"content":"來 給你","from":15.583,"location":2,"to":17.0},{"content":"說好要給你的麵包","from":17.75,"location":2,"to":19.625},{"content":"沒想到你真的住在這裡","from":23.625,"location":2,"to":26.542},{"content":"我還以為你在開玩笑呢","from":26.542,"location":2,"to":28.292},{"content":"學校呢","from":29.958,"location":2,"to":31.292},{"content":"看你的領帶\n應該是小目學園的制服","from":31.292,"location":2,"to":34.958},{"content":"學校…","from":34.958,"location":2,"to":36.542},{"content":"你該不會 連學校在哪都不知道","from":36.542,"location":2,"to":40.083},{"content":"你真的什麼都不記得了","from":42.5,"location":2,"to":45.125},{"content":"這座城市的事呢","from":45.125,"location":2,"to":46.792},{"content":"這裡是\"新京都\"","from":49.458,"location":2,"to":51.417},{"content":"以Build Divide來決定\n政治 經濟 和命運的城市","from":51.417,"location":2,"to":58.292},{"content":"Build Divide越強 越能在市中心\n過著優渥的生活","from":58.292,"location":2,"to":63.125},{"content":"相反的越弱","from":63.125,"location":2,"to":64.417},{"content":"就只能在城市外圍 過著困苦的生活","from":64.417,"location":2,"to":69.208},{"content":"這種社會體制名為","from":69.208,"location":2,"to":71.833},{"content":"\"超民主主義體制\"","from":71.833,"location":2,"to":74.083},{"content":"以Build Divide的優劣\n來維持社會秩序","from":74.083,"location":2,"to":77.792},{"content":"\"某種存在\"","from":77.792,"location":2,"to":79.083},{"content":"藉此統合民眾的想法\n來決定社會進步的方向","from":79.083,"location":2,"to":84.375},{"content":"那個\"存在\"便是我們的目標 \"王\"","from":84.375,"location":2,"to":89.042},{"content":"然後 以Build Divide打倒\"王\"","from":89.042,"location":2,"to":92.417},{"content":"實現自己的夢想","from":92.417,"location":2,"to":94.708},{"content":"而這個戰鬥 我們稱之為\"重構\"","from":94.708,"location":2,"to":99.375},{"content":"(#02 獨自一人的雛鳥)","from":199.875,"location":2,"to":203.417},{"content":"看樣子 這附近沒有其他挑戰者","from":210.75,"location":2,"to":214.042},{"content":"你怎麼知道的","from":214.042,"location":2,"to":215.5},{"content":"那還用問","from":215.5,"location":2,"to":217.417},{"content":"跟戰鬥時一樣 眨眼眨兩次","from":217.417,"location":2,"to":221.125},{"content":"看到了吧\n就是用這個方法看對方的資料","from":222.583,"location":2,"to":227.5},{"content":"這樣 就知道對方是否是挑戰者","from":227.5,"location":2,"to":231.208},{"content":"住在新京都的人\n眼睛裡都安裝了追蹤鏡頭","from":231.208,"location":2,"to":236.458},{"content":"如何 記得嗎","from":238.167,"location":2,"to":239.667},{"content":"沒有印象","from":239.667,"location":2,"to":241.542},{"content":"算了","from":241.542,"location":2,"to":242.958},{"content":"我們先去教職員室\n確認你的學級資…","from":242.958,"location":2,"to":245.792},{"content":"你該不會是倉部同學","from":245.792,"location":2,"to":247.75},{"content":"真的是你","from":247.75,"location":2,"to":249.042},{"content":"我收到你的轉學通知\n但你卻沒來學校過","from":249.042,"location":2,"to":253.125},{"content":"是晚華同學帶他來的嗎","from":254.083,"location":2,"to":256.208},{"content":"是的","from":256.208,"location":2,"to":256.958},{"content":"太好了 你的出席日少到有點危險","from":256.958,"location":2,"to":261.542},{"content":"不行 我不會讓你逃走的","from":261.542,"location":2,"to":265.542},{"content":"他在學校有學級資料","from":265.542,"location":2,"to":268.0},{"content":"應該可以相信他了","from":268.0,"location":2,"to":270.5},{"content":"我們現在需要先知道\n挑戰者的資料","from":270.5,"location":2,"to":273.375},{"content":"我買了新的卡盒","from":274.5,"location":2,"to":276.958},{"content":"不錯啊","from":276.958,"location":2,"to":278.542},{"content":"(挑戰者)\n在哪買的","from":279.25,"location":2,"to":281.417},{"content":"日和 妳看一下嘛","from":281.417,"location":2,"to":283.542},{"content":"西元1600年左右\n傳至日本的Build Divide","from":284.042,"location":2,"to":289.042},{"content":"被長年使用在賭博上","from":289.042,"location":2,"to":292.5},{"content":"到了1950年代","from":292.5,"location":2,"to":294.958},{"content":"當時的娛樂興業公司\"建構之門\"\n進行了科學研究發現…","from":294.958,"location":2,"to":301.917},{"content":"校園裡似乎有挑戰者","from":326.042,"location":2,"to":328.333},{"content":"你有在聽嗎","from":329.083,"location":2,"to":330.333},{"content":"反正贏的人是我","from":330.333,"location":2,"to":331.708},{"content":"那還真可靠啊","from":331.708,"location":2,"to":333.25},{"content":"那麼 去找挑戰者吧","from":333.25,"location":2,"to":335.875},{"content":"原本想 在這裡應該找的到","from":337.25,"location":2,"to":339.25},{"content":"但沒有我想的這麼簡單","from":339.25,"location":2,"to":342.542},{"content":"照人為何想打倒\"王\"","from":343.917,"location":2,"to":347.292},{"content":"反對現在的王\n所提出的\"低等排他主義\"","from":347.292,"location":2,"to":350.333},{"content":"人數還不少","from":350.333,"location":2,"to":352.375},{"content":"你也是其中一員嗎","from":352.375,"location":2,"to":353.958},{"content":"我對這個城市和主張都沒興趣","from":353.958,"location":2,"to":356.292},{"content":"我的願望只有打倒王 就只是這樣","from":356.292,"location":2,"to":359.667},{"content":"那就讓我粉碎你的願望吧","from":359.667,"location":2,"to":363.667},{"content":"妳是誰","from":368.792,"location":2,"to":370.583},{"content":"國中部二年級 棟梨日和","from":370.583,"location":2,"to":373.083},{"content":"跟我… 一決勝負吧","from":373.083,"location":2,"to":377.0},{"content":"她是挑戰者","from":378.583,"location":2,"to":380.667},{"content":"我知道 倉部學長是挑戰者","from":380.667,"location":2,"to":384.75},{"content":"早上看到你時 我就看出來了","from":384.75,"location":2,"to":388.625},{"content":"看你的眼神 你願意接下挑戰了吧","from":388.625,"location":2,"to":392.625},{"content":"那我就收下你的籌碼鑰囉","from":392.625,"location":2,"to":394.958},{"content":"徵求重構","from":394.958,"location":2,"to":396.833},{"content":"確認申請重構","from":399.917,"location":2,"to":402.208},{"content":"請交出籌碼鑰","from":402.208,"location":2,"to":404.75},{"content":"我交出一枚","from":404.75,"location":2,"to":406.083},{"content":"我…","from":410.917,"location":2,"to":412.375},{"content":"交出三枚 全梭","from":412.375,"location":2,"to":414.917},{"content":"等等 你也太毫不猶豫了吧","from":414.917,"location":2,"to":417.083},{"content":"哪有人一上場就全梭的","from":417.083,"location":2,"to":420.167},{"content":"輸了就會失去挑戰資格喔","from":420.167,"location":2,"to":423.25},{"content":"這樣比較有趣","from":423.25,"location":2,"to":425.083},{"content":"真是的","from":425.083,"location":2,"to":426.292},{"content":"重構成立 防護牆展開","from":426.292,"location":2,"to":429.958},{"content":"很適合當我的對手","from":432.042,"location":2,"to":434.042},{"content":"我會全力跟你戰鬥的","from":434.042,"location":2,"to":435.667},{"content":"呼喚 道格拉克","from":435.667,"location":2,"to":437.917},{"content":"呼喚 布魯姆","from":443.125,"location":2,"to":445.292},{"content":"真是的 你真的沒問題吧","from":450.125,"location":2,"to":453.333},{"content":"我先攻","from":453.333,"location":2,"to":454.667},{"content":"學長 我要開始囉","from":454.667,"location":2,"to":456.208},{"content":"Build Divide","from":456.208,"location":2,"to":458.0},{"content":"放置能量","from":458.0,"location":2,"to":459.375},{"content":"召喚 扔擲火藥兵約翰娜","from":459.375,"location":2,"to":462.417},{"content":"直接攻擊學長的生命值","from":462.417,"location":2,"to":465.333},{"content":"一開始就出現破壞事件","from":469.917,"location":2,"to":472.375},{"content":"有沒有後悔 賭上所有的籌碼啊","from":472.375,"location":2,"to":476.375},{"content":"結束了嗎","from":476.375,"location":2,"to":477.875},{"content":"真會逞強","from":477.875,"location":2,"to":479.458},{"content":"回合結束","from":479.458,"location":2,"to":480.833},{"content":"換我了 抽牌","from":480.833,"location":2,"to":482.792},{"content":"放置能量","from":483.25,"location":2,"to":484.583},{"content":"召喚 天眼神槍娜蒂雅","from":484.583,"location":2,"to":487.5},{"content":"攻擊","from":487.5,"location":2,"to":489.042},{"content":"回合結束","from":490.125,"location":2,"to":491.333},{"content":"還擊","from":491.333,"location":2,"to":492.917},{"content":"召喚 尖劍天使阿爾貝爾","from":492.917,"location":2,"to":495.5},{"content":"阿爾貝爾召喚到場上\n約翰娜的力量增加3000","from":496.208,"location":2,"to":499.792},{"content":"約翰娜攻擊娜蒂雅","from":499.792,"location":2,"to":502.125},{"content":"阿爾貝爾攻擊玩家生命值","from":505.375,"location":2,"to":508.208},{"content":"回合結束","from":509.042,"location":2,"to":510.583},{"content":"-留下兩點能量 結束回合\n-換我了","from":510.583,"location":2,"to":513.667},{"content":"在Build Divide中","from":513.667,"location":2,"to":514.875},{"content":"只要還有能量\n即便在對方回合也能採取行動","from":514.875,"location":2,"to":519.208},{"content":"照人 小心點","from":519.208,"location":2,"to":521.5},{"content":"召喚 戰鬥技師威娜","from":521.5,"location":2,"to":524.417},{"content":"其特殊能力能抽一張牌\n並丟棄一張牌","from":524.417,"location":2,"to":527.542},{"content":"再召喚一張威娜","from":527.542,"location":2,"to":529.583},{"content":"抽一張牌 丟棄一張牌","from":529.583,"location":2,"to":532.0},{"content":"兩張威娜攻擊約翰娜和阿爾貝爾","from":532.0,"location":2,"to":535.167},{"content":"可能是陷阱…","from":535.167,"location":2,"to":536.333},{"content":"成功了","from":539.917,"location":2,"to":542.0},{"content":"約翰娜 阿爾貝爾","from":543.5,"location":2,"to":545.125},{"content":"回合結束","from":545.125,"location":2,"to":546.5},{"content":"學長挺厲害的嘛","from":546.5,"location":2,"to":549.25},{"content":"不過 到此為止了","from":549.25,"location":2,"to":550.792},{"content":"我差不多要拿出真實力了","from":550.792,"location":2,"to":552.917},{"content":"斬斷惡運的聖劍 召喚","from":552.917,"location":2,"to":556.792},{"content":"討伐天使 道格拉克","from":556.792,"location":2,"to":559.917},{"content":"領域 建構重現","from":566.333,"location":2,"to":569.0},{"content":"天空要塞","from":584.458,"location":2,"to":586.625},{"content":"這就是她的領域…","from":587.917,"location":2,"to":590.542},{"content":"發動領域能力","from":590.542,"location":2,"to":592.292},{"content":"確認牌組上方兩張牌","from":592.292,"location":2,"to":594.25},{"content":"如裡面有破壞卡的話…","from":594.25,"location":2,"to":596.583},{"content":"就能將其中…","from":596.583,"location":2,"to":599.958},{"content":"就能將其中一張放在場上","from":599.958,"location":2,"to":603.458},{"content":"學長的運氣真好","from":603.458,"location":2,"to":605.583},{"content":"道格拉克不攻擊 結束回合","from":605.583,"location":2,"to":609.375},{"content":"就算攻擊也行啊","from":609.375,"location":2,"to":611.417},{"content":"難道她怕照人反擊嗎","from":611.417,"location":2,"to":613.792},{"content":"那麼她不攻擊 又將牌卡直立放置","from":613.792,"location":2,"to":617.333},{"content":"(可鎖定 不可鎖定)\n應該是為了引誘敵方鎖定目標","from":617.333,"location":2,"to":619.625},{"content":"來 這樣就能鎖定道格拉克囉","from":619.625,"location":2,"to":622.625},{"content":"果然沒錯","from":622.625,"location":2,"to":623.958},{"content":"哪有這樣自爆的","